<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:12:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，英国犹太人为在加沙被扣押的以色列人质举行集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</link><description>反犹太主义袭击增加了 1,350% 以上，犹太教堂和犹太学校加强了安全措施，但这并没有阻止大量英国犹太人参加周日在伦敦特拉法加广场举行的示威活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关闭半岛电视台在当地的业务是否正确？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</link><description>半岛电视台正在呼应哈马斯的信息，并且在报道上疏忽大意，但这是否证明以色列政府有理由关闭该电视台的运作——正如沙特阿拉伯、埃及和伊拉克已经所做的那样？</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷两家豪华酒店拒绝接待遭受哈马斯袭击的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-jerusalem-luxury-hotels-refuse-to-house-israelis-struck-by-hamas/0000018b-5bf9-d473-a5fb-7ff991c90000</link><description>阿尔弗雷德·阿基洛夫拒绝向因战争而流离失所的数千名以色列人开放马米拉和大卫城堡酒店的大门；他的解释是：缺乏人手。他还拒绝了旅游部提供的帮助招聘员工的帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-jerusalem-luxury-hotels-refuse-to-house-israelis-struck-by-hamas/0000018b-5bf9-d473-a5fb-7ff991c90000</guid></item><item><title>为什么右翼美国不是以色列的真正盟友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-right-wing-america-is-no-real-ally-for-israel/0000018b-5bfd-d00f-a9bf-7bfdd4ae0000</link><description>对于美国右翼专家和政客来说，煽动反对拜登、移民和穆斯林远比真正声援以色列人和支持以色列安全重要得多</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-right-wing-america-is-no-real-ally-for-israel/0000018b-5bfd-d00f-a9bf-7bfdd4ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列能否从最可怕的噩梦中醒来并采取正确的行动？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-israel-wake-up-from-its-worst-nightmare-and-do-the-right-thing/0000018b-56e0-d2b2-addf-76f84b5d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-israel-wake-up-from-its-worst-nightmare-and-do-the-right-thing/0000018b-56e0-d2b2-addf-76f84b5d0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再警告，以色列军队忽视了加沙边境发生故障的观测气球</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/despite-warnings-idf-neglected-malfunctioning-observation-balloons-on-gaza-border/0000018b-5b84-d8e2-a1eb-fb96f45b0000</link><description>仍在运行的所有四个气球都遭到哈马斯的攻击并击落，操作它们的士兵（现在集中在数量较少的操作室中）无法传递信息并警告部队</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/despite-warnings-idf-neglected-malfunctioning-observation-balloons-on-gaza-border/0000018b-5b84-d8e2-a1eb-fb96f45b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，哈马斯在加沙扣押了 222 名人质，其中包括“相当多”外国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</link><description>美国报道称，拜登政府建议以色列推迟对加沙的地面入侵，以利于人质获释 ■ 土耳其在袭击以色列后要求哈马斯领导人离开其领土 ■ 以色列国防军表示，已通知 222 名人质家属，其中包括“相当多”外国人 ■ 以色列国防军袭击真主党据点，北部边境局势再度紧张 ■ 第三批前往加沙的援助物资经埃及进入拉法过境点 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：4,380 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，13,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，以色列正奔向道德深渊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</guid></item><item><title>15万枚导弹瞄准以色列：真主党的致命武器库能达到多远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有深入以色列境内的火箭和远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 07:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势加剧，以色列军队等待入侵加沙的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-awaits-order-for-gaza-invasion-as-middle-east-tensions-sear/0000018b-58f5-dd05-a7bf-ffffe0550000</link><description>随着伊朗试图针对以色列和美国的利益、也门叛乱分子向以色列发射导弹以及真主党使边境升温，美国在该地区部署了大量军事存在。内塔尼亚胡的圈子传达的信息是，最好不要急于进入加沙，担心发生大规模火灾</description><pubDat