无法面对现实。这就是为什么他们不给我们任何希望</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 20:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-22/ty-article/.highlight/for-netanyahu-and-his-cronies-life-and-death-are-just-a-photo-op/0000018b-5857-d2b2-addf-7e7f71dc0000</guid></item><item><title>研究人员推断，西班牙的尼安德特人引发了火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</link><description>我们知道古人类使用火已有数十万年，甚至超过一百万年，但他们能点燃火吗？尼安德特人可以</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</guid></item><item><title>数千名艺术界人士发出信函谴责以色列，但没有提及哈马斯的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</link><description>艺术家、画廊主和其他艺术界成员发表了这封公开信，其中展示了一位嘲笑以色列人质的艺术家的作品。超过 2000 名艺术家（其中大多数是以色列人）回应道：“你让我们所有人失去人性”</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</guid></item></channel></rss>